				<h1>About</h1>
			</div>

			<p>This is a Kinyarwanda &#8660; English dictionary created to help people who are learning either language.
			What makes it different to other dictionaries is that the software has been designed
			for a Bantu language. Words are stored with prefixes, stems and modifiers, so it allows you to search
			for different forms of the same word. You can search for singular forms and plural forms of nouns, and
			present tense or past tense forms of verbs.</p>

